cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on object detection and 3D pose estimation in images, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves training a Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) to predict normalization parameters, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the method is for robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) tasks, specifically for 3D pose estimation.
